cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

The paper deals with obstacle detection using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of synthetic images for training the network is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and the use of deep neural networks is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE).
